{"tid":1267250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當你面對中共極權國家機器感到絕望無助","createTime":"2019-06-29T19:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T10:27:07.000Z","uid":33875,"like":122,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dce4dceb0acf6b1272542d9d4a72310272932d67","tid":1267250,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/39hTNSSh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F39hTNSSh.png&h=80ace159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上圖係中國年幾前係哈薩克同俄羅斯開會，中方隨行官員遲到，導致習近平孤毒應戰既尷尬畫面，更被普京笑稱<strong>「Lone Warrior」</strong>，中俄關埋門總算兩兄弟，大家靜靜地唔講出去，飛機會議係國際上好快就無人記得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/s52d4m6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs52d4m6h.jpg&h=46801853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不幸地，係前日G20中日會面，習總被同行官員Prank多次。<strong>無助既習總就好似百人斬既AV女優一樣被一群日本壯老包圍住。</strong><br />\n<br />\n泱泱大國竟然容許如此重大國恥一再發生，而且對方係一直被利用作控制民族歸屬感而妖魔化既日本。出席既都係中委會高官要員，花費大量人力物力去推動成事，尤其係貿易戰期間更要謹慎周詳，結果就係出錯，鬧出笑話。<br />\n<br />\n中共並非牢不可破，佢地會誤判、會出錯，好抱歉我無辦法話你知佢地幾時會係香港問題上再犯錯，但我唔係叫大家守株待兔，我地需要不斷敲打高牆，直到某日我地搵到一條小裂痕。<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">所以，先留住你既生命，我地好需要你漫長既時間同微薄既力量。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1aadb0c2417ed0e0e3569f89621e829c17363d45","tid":1267250,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好絕望...."},{"pid":"369bf266b6dbaad39448819faeacfe030ad18832","tid":1267250,"uid":103325,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:13:29.000Z","msg":"留住條命，每一個人都好有用<br />\n大家要用自己嘅選票，去將建制踢出議會"},{"pid":"1a697fd743c4c0c8870bece8e0eeb5f3cb9272fd","tid":1267250,"uid":227635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:16:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要留住條命<br />\n仲要同佢鬥命硬 鬥長命！"},{"pid":"1bd3872b1b6605c90642cdcc939eb8e1cbcd3a93","tid":1267250,"uid":33875,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1aadb0c2417ed0e0e3569f89621e829c17363d45","tid":1267250,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好絕望...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:21:16.000Z","msg":"經過咁多年抗爭，相信無人有把握話到比大家知點贏。或者大家寄望過69、612、616、621，好多死線定咗比政府，同時定咗比自己。<br />\n<br />\n當政府拖延處理，抗爭者就會失望、絕望。我地要接受抗爭係漫長而艱苦，但唔代表我地唔需要每一次都盡力，只係心態上要抽離，唔可以對一次行動得失放太重情感。"},{"pid":"f42cbc49bc685a4828b9fb5c4b3021361f985183","tid":1267250,"uid":33875,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QbYNqO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QbYNqO.gif&h=ebe8f594&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5148bd87722e8709b64d4e0a3a4f82ad8f463f4a","tid":1267250,"uid":260797,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T20:00:45.000Z","msg":"唔知中共幾時先冧檔﹐變成民主中國﹐領導人及所有官員係人民投票選嘅﹐唔強逼普教中﹐言論新聞網絡自由唔使再翻牆﹐好天真呀我"},{"pid":"3e69fabaefec8a1ab5c8f7e313c43fc01ecdbe17","tid":1267250,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T20:01:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">習敗北</span></span>"},{"pid":"48f977ad62c159bfb425f65cbb12928da6c793ed","tid":1267250,"uid":64884,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T20:11:58.000Z","msg":"話說